{"tid":1576233,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果火魔法誤中自己友","createTime":"2019-09-17T06:59:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T16:11:16.000Z","uid":90486,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8300a836000bde9dd9af5daa801767d4109b2cba","tid":1576233,"uid":90486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:59:58.000Z","msg":"Q：身上著火時，怎麼辦？<br />\nA：被火燒到時，一定要牢記下面步驟：<br />\n（一）停：立刻停在原地。<br />\n（二）躺：就地躺下，立刻雙手摀在臉上（減少顏面傷殘機會）。如果雙手著火，則將手平貼大腿。<br />\n（三）滾：然後左右翻滾直到火勢熄滅。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以防萬一</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eTax5ur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeTax5ur.jpg&h=b97ec2a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHQ6qus.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHQ6qus.jpg&h=c25f09f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"072a61709e02bf59daa326ad812116d1d775c3e5","tid":1576233,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"ce164ef7b17a27a7adfb11657ee817fef780ddf1","tid":1576233,"uid":90486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:02:01.000Z","msg":"自推，免得有意外發生大家唔識處理"},{"pid":"30c0b383126151c9091ea40885d75762a2ff50ec","tid":1576233,"uid":90486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:03:41.000Z","msg":